Monday, November 28 Sibahle helps Ayanda make a major decision about his paternity. MaNgcobo worries that something wrong has happened to Mxolisi. Mxolisi comes to a dead end. Tuesday, November 29 Smangele feels humiliated when Ayanda vanishes. Mxolisi and MaNgcobo s secret comes back to haunt them. Sibahle and Ayanda struggle to stay apart. Wednesday, November 30 Ayanda is told by MamKhulu that he should stop fighting his nature because the Xulu family understands the function of polygamy and embrace it. Mondli realises his feelings for Nosipho haven t died, but Nosipho tells him something heartbreaking. Mxolisi gets a call from a client about a job bringing them out of the shadows.